					<h2><a href="http://driftervagabond.wordpress.com/2013/06/09/bitcoin-tip/" rel="bookmark">Bitcoin tip</a></h2>
				</div>
				<div class="post-1575 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-travel tag-bitcoin tag-bitcoins-travel tag-blog-tipping tag-solo-travel tag-travel">
					<div class="entry">
					<p><a href="http://driftervagabond.files.wordpress.com/2013/06/bitcointip2.png"><img src="http://driftervagabond.files.wordpress.com/2013/06/bitcointip2.png?w=500" alt="bitcointip"   class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1582" /></a></p>
<p> </p>
<p> </p>
<p> </p>
<p>I&#8217;ve been having fun with bitcoins recently, the QR code above can be scanned with a smartphone and will instruct a bitcoin payment provider like CoinBase etc to leave a 10cent tip. Pretty amazing&#8230;&#8230;&#8230;.</p>
					</div>
					<div class="postinfo">
						<p class="com"><a href="http://driftervagabond.wordpress.com/2013/06/09/bitcoin-tip/#comments" title="Comment on Bitcoin tip">1 Comment</a></p>
