				<div class="post-1551 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-travel tag-around-the-world tag-beijing tag-bitcoin tag-bitcoins-travel tag-cambodia tag-chengdu tag-china tag-chungking-mansions tag-guangxi tag-guilin tag-halong-bay tag-ho-chi-minh tag-hong-kong tag-kuala-lumpur tag-kunming tag-round-the-world tag-saigon tag-solo-travel tag-st-petersburg tag-trans-siberian tag-travel tag-vietnam tag-xian tag-yangshuo tag-yunnan">
					<div class="entry">
					<p>Hi there,</p>
<p>I&#8217;m now accepting bitcoin donations for the blog at:</p>
<p>1Mi4CtDXrkGWMQg7LqoDWmceFCLgJjYUk4</p>
<p> </p>
<p>I don&#8217;t honestly expect to make any money but bitcoins have become my latest obsession, they are, after all, the next &#8220;big thing&#8221;. Remember, you heard it here first.</p>
<p> </p>
<p><a title="Learn about bitcoins" href="http://http://lovebitcoins.org/" target="_blank">http://lovebitcoins.org/</a></p>
