					<small>Posted by: <strong>drifter,vagabond</strong> | February 8, 2012 </small>
					<h2><a href="http://driftervagabond.wordpress.com/2012/02/08/another-grovelling-apology/" rel="bookmark">Another grovelling apology</a></h2>
				</div>
				<div class="post-1488 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-travel">
					<div class="entry">
					<p>Updates coming soon, tune in two weeks from now&#8230;&#8230;&#8230;.</p>
					</div>
					<div class="postinfo">
						<p class="com"><a href="http://driftervagabond.wordpress.com/2012/02/08/another-grovelling-apology/#respond" title="Comment on Another grovelling apology">Leave a Comment</a></p>
						<p>Posted in <a href="http://driftervagabond.wordpress.com/category/travel/" rel="category tag">Travel</a> </p>
